{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "Update App Versions",
  "description": "Automates updating app version, UIKit version, and Call SDK version across all files. Creates a branch, makes changes, and creates a PR.",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "when": {
    "type": "userTriggered"
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "The user wants to update app versions. Follow this interactive workflow:\n\n**PHASE 0: LINEAR TICKET (Optional)**\nAsk: \"Do you have a Linear ticket for this update? (Enter ticket ID like ENG-123, or 'skip' to continue without one)\"\n\n- If user provides ticket ID: Validate it exists using Linear MCP, use for branch name\n- If 'skip': Continue without Linear integration\n\n**PHASE 1: GATHER CURRENT VERSIONS**\nRead these files to get current versions:\n- package.json (version, cometChatCustomConfig.version, @cometchat/chat-uikit-react, @cometchat/calls-sdk-javascript)\n- src/CometChat/context/CometChatContext.tsx (chatBuilderVersion)\n- README.md (version badge, npm install command)\n- NEXT_JS.md (version badge, npm install command)\n\n**PHASE 2: ASK FOR NEW VERSIONS (One at a time)**\n\n1. Show: \"Current App Version: X.X.X\" → Ask: \"New app version?\" (or 'same' to skip)\n   - Updates: package.json version, cometChatCustomConfig.version, CometChatContext.tsx chatBuilderVersion, README.md badge, NEXT_JS.md badge\n\n2. Show: \"Current UIKit Version (@cometchat/chat-uikit-react): X.X.X\" → Ask: \"New UIKit version?\" (or 'same' to skip)\n   - Updates: package.json dependency, README.md npm install command, NEXT_JS.md npm install command\n\n3. Show: \"Current Call SDK Version (@cometchat/calls-sdk-javascript): X.X.X\" → Ask: \"New Call SDK version?\" (or 'same' to skip)\n   - Updates: package.json dependency, README.md npm install command, NEXT_JS.md npm install command\n\n4. Auto-generate branch name based on Linear ticket or versions. Ask: \"Branch name: X - OK? (or type different name)\"\n\n**PHASE 3: PREVIEW & CONFIRM**\nShow summary table:\n| Component | Current | New | Files Updated |\n|-----------|---------|-----|---------------|\n| App Version | X.X.X | Y.Y.Y | package.json, CometChatContext.tsx, README.md, NEXT_JS.md |\n| UIKit | X.X.X | Y.Y.Y | package.json, README.md, NEXT_JS.md |\n| Call SDK | X.X.X | Y.Y.Y | package.json, README.md, NEXT_JS.md |\n\nAsk: \"Proceed with these changes? (yes/no)\"\n\n**PHASE 4: EXECUTE CHANGES**\n1. Stash uncommitted changes if any\n2. Checkout main and pull latest\n3. Create new branch\n4. Update all files:\n   - package.json: version, cometChatCustomConfig.version, dependencies\n   - src/CometChat/context/CometChatContext.tsx: chatBuilderVersion variable\n   - README.md: version badge URL and npm install command\n   - NEXT_JS.md: version badge URL and npm install command\n5. Show git diff\n6. Ask: \"Changes look correct? Commit and push? (yes/no)\"\n7. Commit with message: \"chore: bump app to vX.X.X, uikit X.X.X, call-sdk X.X.X\" (prefix with ticket ID if exists)\n8. Push branch to origin\n9. Create PR to main using GitHub MCP with:\n   - Title: \"chore: Update versions - app vX.X.X, uikit X.X.X\"\n   - Body: List all version changes and files modified\n10. If Linear ticket exists, add PR link as comment\n11. Share PR link with user\n\n**ERROR HANDLING**\n- If Linear fails: Continue without it, inform user\n- If git fails: Show error, ask how to proceed\n- If PR creation fails: Provide manual gh command\n\n**TIPS**\n- User can say 'same', 'skip', or 'no change' to keep current version\n- Suggest next patch version for app version (e.g., 1.0.21 → 1.0.22)"
  }
}
